ligns with these statements, demonstrating a high level of grounding in the provided context.', 'confidence_score': 0.9, 'citations': [{'source': 'Ebook-Agentic-AI.pdf', 'chunk_id': 3}, {'source': 'Ebook-Agentic-AI.pdf', 'chunk_id': 19}, {'source': 'Ebook-Agentic-AI.pdf', 'chunk_id': 8}, {'source': 'Ebook-Agentic-AI.pdf', 'chunk_id': 31}, {'source': 'Ebook-Agentic-AI.pdf', 'chunk_id': 42}], 'agent_trace': [{'agent': 'input_guardrails', 'status': 'passed', 'timestamp': '2026-05-29 12:55:25.712715'}, {'agent': 'planner', 'status': 'completed', 'timestamp': '2026-05-29 12:55:26.318849'}, {'agent': 'retriever', 'status': 'completed', 'timestamp': '2026-05-29 12:55:26.646141'}, {'agent': 'synthesizer', 'status': 'completed', 'timestamp': '2026-05-29 12:55:27.431814'}, {'agent': 'output_guardrails', 'status': 'passed', 'timestamp': '2026-05-29 12:55:27.435383'}, {'agent': 'verifier', 'status': 'completed', 'timestamp': '2026-05-29 12:55:28.549408'}], 'is_safe': True, 'blocked_reason': None}
